query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `panelist_feedback` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `interviewId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `panelistId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `userId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `overallRating` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `technicalSkills` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `communicationSkills` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `problemSolving` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cultureFit` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `strengths` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `weaknesses` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `notes` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `recommendation` enum('strong_hire','hire','no_hire','strong_no_hire') DEFAULT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `interviewId` (`interviewId`),
  KEY `panelistId` (`panelistId`),
  KEY `userId` (`userId`)
);
